# Vault content — never commit personal knowledge base data.
# Anchored to repo root so it doesn't collide with the Go package
# at cli/internal/vault or the Swift module at
# app/Sources/SecondBrainCore/Vault (both tracked).
/vault/
# .2ndbrain/ holds the SQLite index.db, bench.db, models/, recovery/, logs/ —
# machine-local derived state, never commit. (git has no trailing-inline-comment
# support, so this comment must sit on its own line above the bare pattern.)
.2ndbrain/
